{"tid":1524692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果黨鐵所有閘口既八達通讀卡位都爆晒點算？","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T00:10:12.000Z","uid":49669,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8496afa7ace7e0f66bfc437522f894eedcf5aa05","tid":1524692,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:54:05.000Z","msg":"入飛位又咁啱有AA膠痴住入唔到卡Wor，到時想返工都難了，諗起都覺得慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b1b871e78c823fc0f29afd0ac0bc5da1236547","tid":1524692,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2525d1f16e75192ae2aa5c33d1ccf08220b57957","tid":1524692,"uid":60398,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:48:46.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c24413ba7e52a726538e93ac5a62b43268aeb8ac","tid":1524692,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bb5eba61f1aa27db3e5b963e4363500c559479","tid":1524692,"uid":143699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:35:37.000Z","msg":"大家冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上今晚黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n完整示範片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70udFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=4bf3ee9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"3c65c75e48f69c46088e8669235c5b969d66cdff","tid":1524692,"uid":42250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:43:18.000Z","msg":"會好似催淚彈咁<br />\n拎啲過期嘅出嚟用"},{"pid":"509c5e282b5f2eeea775ad86ec81b36fb396ca70","tid":1524692,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:10:12.000Z","msg":"破卡蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />換個蓋就可以，如果破碎啲板就。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但緊急維修，料又貴，料又未必有<br />\n係咁日日壞，<br />\n你想做死班技術人員咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}